Brenda wants to have a picnic -> Brenda quiere tener un picnic.
She gets a basket -> Ella obtiene una canasta
She puts sandwiches in the basket -> Ella pone sándwiches en la canasta.
The sandwiches are healthy -> Los sándwiches son sanos.
They are also tasty -> Son sabrosos también
She drives to the park -> Ella conduce al parque
She lays out a blanket -> Extiende una cobija
She hears a sound -> Escucha un sonido
It is raining -> Está lloviendo
She folds the blanket back -> Dobla la manta hacia atrás
She puts the food in the basket -> Ella pone la comida en la canasta

